## Trade-Off Matrix (document decisions)

| Decision | Chosen approach | Rationale |
|----------|-----------------|-----------|
| Grid data window | Server pagination + row virtualization | Bounded memory; works at 20k+ scale; sort/filter stay server-side |
| vs infinite scroll | Pagination | Predictable UX; easier RBAC filtering; simpler cache invalidation |
| Document load | Streaming / page-range fetch | Full download of 1 GB doc is unacceptable on client |
| Split/merge | Server job + polling/WebSocket mock | Long-running; cancel/retry; consistent state |
| RBAC enforcement | Backend primary, frontend UX | Security at API; UI prevents confusion |
| Server vs client state | TanStack Query + Zustand | Query for server data; Zustand for ephemeral UI only |
| Mutations | Pessimistic for delete/split/merge; optimistic for comments | Reliability over snappiness for destructive/long ops |

